  "description": "Adds multiple new animal based origins to the game.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">NOTE: This is a addon for the origin mod.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod requires the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/origins\">origin mod</a>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pehkui\">pehkui mod.</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Origins give you different abilities that affect the way you play the game in different ways depending on what origin you chose.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod adds 9 new animal based origins to the game!&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Info about the origins in the pictures.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ORIGINS:&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Duck</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Gecko</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Giraffe</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Grasshopper</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Lizard</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Shark</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Sheep</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Red Panda</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Cat</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/uy9QFaQWR7\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_DISCORD.png\" alt=\"discord\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Discord server:&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/uy9QFaQWR7\">https://discord.gg/uy9QFaQWR7</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_PROMO.png\" alt=\"hosting\"/></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Want to host your own server?&nbsp; &nbsp; Use code: CHILLZONE for 25% off your first month!&nbsp;<br /><strong><em><a class=\"anchor-3Z-8Bb anchorUnderlineOnHover-2ESHQB\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\" role=\"button\" href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone</a>&nbsp;</em></strong></p>",
